Stay Charged on the Go - Power up your devices effortlessly with the built-in USB and USB C charging port in carry on luggage. No more worrying about low batteries while traveling! (Power bank not included).

Stylish and Durable - Crafted from premium materials, this ultra lightweight luggage features a textured finish, shielding it from scratches. LUGGEX luggage remains sleek and scuff-free, exuding elegance wherever you go.

Convenient Accessory Bag - The 14-inch bag features an elastic strap that effortlessly attaches to the handle, keeping your essentials easily accessible. Enjoy the convenience of having your belongings at hand and say goodbye to rummaging through your suitcase!

Organized Convenience - Rose gold carry on suitcase is thoughtfully designed with 3 large zippered dividers and enclosed compartments. Enjoy the convenience of a neatly organized suitcase after every flight, making packing and unpacking a breeze.

Quality Assurance - We stand behind the excellence of rose gold luggage and offer a free 3-year warranty for your peace of mind. Should you encounter any issues, our dedicated customer service team will respond promptly within 12 hours.

How do I set the code when I first get it? 1.Turn the dials to the correct combination.(0-0-0) 2. Press down the button by a tool, set the new combination (e.g.:8-8-8), then pull the square part. 3. Lock the case again, and now you can open the lock with the new combination. If the luggage I received was damaged, who can I look for? We promise that every Luggex luggage will go through strict quality inspection before shipping. LuggeX claims to will keep the luggage in repair for 3 years. Please feel free to let us know and the related team will respond within 12H. How to use the charging port? 1. Unzip the luggage and find the cable inside. 2. Charge it with a power bank. (The USB-A input only works for USB-A output) 3. Open the outside charge port and connect it with a cable, then connect it to your phone. Can the 14-inch cosmetic bag be securely attached to the luggage handle? Yes. The cosmetic case with zippered compartment can keep your valuables close at hand and it has an elastic strap that keeps it secure on the suitcase handle. Does the suitcase have a dual-zippered mesh compartment? Yes. The suitcase with dual-zippered mesh compartments provides two large packing spaces equipped with additional packing compartments. Keep your belongings organized and pristine throughout your journey.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Large light weight suitcase
reviews.reviewText: Although I have not used this suitcase yet, I purchased it based on lots of positive reviews. It is light weight, the zippers work well, it is expandable, I like the 2 zippered halves - all important to me. The one critique I will give is that it is advertised as rose gold - this is not. It is more pink than rose gold. I am disappointed in this fact, yet I have decided to keep it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Plenty of room
reviews.reviewText: I love that there’s plenty of room in both luggage even though they are small. It’s perfect for what I need. I especially like that it has zipped up covers for both sides that way nothing moves around or falls out. Now I need to get the bigger one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to move, either standing up or pulling on handle, like all the pockets inside
reviews.reviewText: It is very easy to move, either standing up or pulling on handle. I like all the pockets inside very much. On our trip, we thought we would use the usb charging feature, but we've actually not had to charge from it at all yet. It would be nice if the wheels had a locking mechanism on a pair of the wheelsets, so that we aren't having to chase the suitcase on what we thought was a level flat surface. It is just the right size for a 3-night adventure trip! Love it.
